<br></li><li> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fluid movement system</h2> gives a high degree of traversal freedom from the get go. Double jumps and dashes that can be later upgraded and infused with special traits. <br><br></li><li> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\">100 of upgrades</h2> that can drastically change the playstyle <br><br></li><li> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Powerful power-ups</h2> that may help you win the hardest of the battles<br><br></li><li> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Weird Enemies</h2> creatures from different worlds corrupted by the Mists. <br><br></li><li> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Combos system</h2> for showing off style and mastery<br><br></li><li> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\">12 unique magic weapons </h2> each with two distinct fire modes that have strength and weakness of their own</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/937870/extras/tumblr_pcira8UE1R1si4jeeo3_500.gif?t=1709490604\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Hard Start","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/937870/6d60be553a97da5bc80edeedd108dc7d463f7e7f.jpg"},{"name":"The Ritual ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/937870/0f8022ec8547491856a09ddec75cd4380df7553c.jpg"},{"name":"I'll be back!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/937870/797e0c2fa50229b79230409f4ea129e7a17208a7.jpg"},{"name":"Legion Fall","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/937870/8ac87d695c23a5c8eb9954664ee9e0b124cdf485.jpg"},{"name":"Airborne","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/937870/b392eb4d884d0db8ff2603ceb450b0f58583f502.jpg"},{"name":"Turreted Madness","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/937870/9c8909349cb1c42bcd365646e5a5d84946e4361d.jpg"},{"name":"Mistable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/93787